    <entry>
      <title>写博客第一步，熟悉Markdown语法和编辑器</title>
      <link href="/2020031020.html"/>
      <url>/2020031020.html</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<link rel="stylesheet" class="aplayer-secondary-style-marker" href="/assets/css/APlayer.min.css"><script src="/assets/js/APlayer.min.js" class="aplayer-secondary-script-marker"></script><script class="meting-secondary-script-marker" src="/assets/js/Meting.min.js"></script><h1>什么是Markdown</h1><blockquote><p>Markdown由<a href="https://daringfireball.net/projects/markdown/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">John Gruber</a>于2004年创建，是一种轻量级的标记语言，可用于将格式设置元素添加到纯文本文档中。</p></blockquote><p>Markdown最大的优点大概就是简单直观，但对于只熟悉Word打字的人来说，在.md文件中修改文字的格式可能会是一头雾水。首先让我们熟悉Markdown的基本语法，你就会明白Markdown为什么好用。</p><p><a href="https://www.markdownguide.org/tools/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">*哪些应用支持markdown?</a></p><h1>Markdown的基本语法</h1><p><a href="https://tool.lu/zh_CN/markdown/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">*立刻打开在线版本体验？边练边学？</a>（特易挑了个没广告的）</p><p>首次接触者注意⚠️ 所有的符号均为英文字符，有无空格需格外注意。</p><blockquote><h2 id="1-标题">1. 标题</h2><div class="code-area-wrap"><div class="highlight-tools"><i class="fa fa-angle-down code-expand" aria-hidden="true"></i><div class="code_lang">markdown</div><div class="copy-notice"></div><i class="fa fa-clipboard" aria-hidden="true"></i></div><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="section"># 一级标题</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div><p>几个#就是几级标题，最多支持6级标题，标题不仅字大小不同，还可以帮助你生成目录。注意#和字中间要有空格。</p><h2 id="2-文字格式">2. 文字格式</h2><div class="code-area-wrap"><div class="highlight-tools"><i class="fa fa-angle-down code-expand" aria-hidden="true"></i><div class="code_lang">markdown</div><div class="copy-notice"></div><i class="fa fa-clipboard" aria-hidden="true"></i></div><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="strong">**加粗**</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="emphasis">*斜体*</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="strong">***加粗斜体**</span>*</span><br><span class="line">~~哇，我被划掉了~~</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div><h2 id="3-为文字添加超链接">3. 为文字添加超链接</h2><div class="code-area-wrap"><div class="highlight-tools"><i class="fa fa-angle-down code-expand" aria-hidden="true"></i><div class="code_lang">markdown</div><div class="copy-notice"></div><i class="fa fa-clipboard" aria-hidden="true"></i></div><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">[<span class="string">要去的地方</span>](<span class="link">超链接</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div><h2 id="4-插入图片">4. 插入图片</h2><div class="code-area-wrap"><div class="highlight-tools"><i class="fa fa-angle-down code-expand" aria-hidden="true"></i><div class="code_lang">markdown</div><div class="copy-notice"></div><i class="fa fa-clipboard" aria-hidden="true"></i></div><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">![<span class="string">图片alt</span>](<span class="link">图片链接 "图片提示"</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div><p>图片alt是图片下文字，有点像图名；图片提示是指鼠标移动到图片上显示的文字。下面是演示：</p><a href="https://cn.bing.com/th?id=OIP.c44wrYEMpGtoI17Sgbsg1gAAAA&amp;pid=Api&amp;rs=1" data-fancybox="group" data-caption="点我点我" class="fancybox"><img alt="点我点我" title="点我点我" style="zoom:50%;" data-src="https://cn.bing.com/th?id=OIP.c44wrYEMpGtoI17Sgbsg1gAAAA&amp;pid=Api&amp;rs=1" src="/img/loading.gif" class="lazyload"></a><h2 id="5-分割线">5. 分割线</h2><div class="code-area-wrap"><div class="highlight-tools"><i class="fa fa-angle-down code-expand" aria-hidden="true"></i><div class="code_lang">markdown</div><div class="copy-notice"></div><i class="fa fa-clipboard" aria-hidden="true"></i></div><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">---</span><br><span class="line"><span class="emphasis">***</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div><p>选-或者*都可以。</p><h2 id="6-引用">6. 引用</h2><div class="code-area-wrap"><div class="highlight-tools"><i class="fa fa-angle-down code-expand" aria-hidden="true"></i><div class="code_lang">markdown</div><div class="copy-notice"></div><i class="fa fa-clipboard" aria-hidden="true"></i></div><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&gt;名人名言</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div><h2 id="7-代码">7. 代码</h2><div class="code-area-wrap"><div class="highlight-tools"><i class="fa fa-angle-down code-expand" aria-hidden="true"></i><div class="code_lang">markdown</div><div class="copy-notice"></div><i class="fa fa-clipboard" aria-hidden="true"></i></div><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="code">`代码`</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div><div class="code-area-wrap"><div class="highlight-tools"><i class="fa fa-angle-down code-expand" aria-hidden="true"></i><div class="code_lang">markdown</div><div class="copy-notice"></div><i class="fa fa-clipboard" aria-hidden="true"></i></div><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="code">```</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">代码块</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">```</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div><h2 id="8-表格">8. 表格</h2><div class="code-area-wrap"><div class="highlight-tools"><i class="fa fa-angle-down code-expand" aria-hidden="true"></i><div class="code_lang">ruby</div><div class="copy-notice"></div><i class="fa fa-clipboard" aria-hidden="true"></i></div><figure class="highlight ruby"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">Aa<span class="params">|BbBb|</span>cc<span class="params">|</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="params">--|</span><span class="symbol">:--</span><span class="symbol">:|--</span><span class="symbol">:</span></span><br><span class="line">aa<span class="params">|bbbb|</span>cc</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div><h2 id="9-列表">9. 列表</h2><p>带上标记号的列表，也可用- 或 +</p><div class="code-area-wrap"><div class="highlight-tools"><i class="fa fa-angle-down code-expand" aria-hidden="true"></i><div class="code_lang">markdown</div><div class="copy-notice"></div><i class="fa fa-clipboard" aria-hidden="true"></i></div><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="bullet">* </span>A</span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">* </span>B</span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">* </span>C</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div><p>有序号的列表</p><div class="code-area-wrap"><div class="highlight-tools"><i class="fa fa-angle-down code-expand" aria-hidden="true"></i><div class="code_lang">markdown</div><div class="copy-notice"></div><i class="fa fa-clipboard" aria-hidden="true"></i></div><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="bullet">1. </span>A</span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">2. </span>B</span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">3. </span>B</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div></blockquote><p>你也可以打开上面那个看着像广告的链接，边打边体验。</p><p>有疑问？前往下面的疑问。</p><h1>Markdown的更多语法</h1><p>可以先去这回顾一下 》》》<a href="https://www.markdownguide.org/basic-syntax/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">官方基本语法说明</a></p><p>先挖个坑，看啥时候有空汇总其它的语法。</p><p>你也可以先去啃官网的<a href="https://www.markdownguide.org/extended-syntax/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">扩增语法说明</a>。</p><h1>疑问❓</h1><h2 id="1-为什么好像不能把文字居中？">1. <a href="https://www.zhihu.com/question/25909518/answer/31669314" target="_blank" rel="noopener">为什么好像不能把文字居中？</a></h2><p>但是，我发现好像还是可以居中的。</p><p align="center">我能居中啦～～～～</p><blockquote><p>不过，这似乎并不是通过markdown语法实现的，而是使用内嵌html标签的方式做到的？</p><p>代码见下方⬇️</p></blockquote><div class="code-area-wrap"><div class="highlight-tools"><i class="fa fa-angle-down code-expand" aria-hidden="true"></i><div class="code_lang">Code</div><div class="copy-notice"></div><i class="fa fa-clipboard" aria-hidden="true"></i></div><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;p align&#x3D;&quot;center&quot;&gt;哈哈&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;p align&#x3D;&quot;left&quot;&gt;我能&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;p align&#x3D;&quot;right&quot;&gt;左右横跳&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div><h2 id="2-emoji怎么加？">2. emoji怎么加？</h2><div class="code-area-wrap"><div class="highlight-tools"><i class="fa fa-angle-down code-expand" aria-hidden="true"></i><div class="code_lang">Code</div><div class="copy-notice"></div><i class="fa fa-clipboard" aria-hidden="true"></i></div><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">:emoji name:</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div><p>就是这么简单！而它们的名字可以<a href="https://emojipedia.org/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在这</a>获取！</p><p>在编辑器里打表情可以更方便，往下看！</p><h2 id="3-翻车了！emoji在Hexo默认渲染器下无法显示！">3. 翻车了！emoji在Hexo默认渲染器下无法显示！</h2><p>上<a href="https://blog.csdn.net/weixin_41287260/article/details/103050545" target="_blank" rel="noopener">这</a>看看，几步轻松搞定这个问题。</p><h1>Markdown语法编辑器</h1><p>你完全可以使用vim编辑器或者其他任何文本编辑器来编写.md文件，但是有一个好的编辑器，可以使效果实时可见，语法高亮变色，这会方便很多！</p><p>刚开始我使用Visual Studio Code来编写(别问我为什么)，还是可以显示语法的，后来想找个可以实时预览的，没想到Visual Studio Code就可以而我没发现，点击图中右侧的第一个图标就可以啦！或者使用command/ctrl+K 然后按v就可以啦。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/LucasX21s/img_for_blog/blog/img/demo5.png" data-fancybox="group" data-caption class="fancybox"><img alt title data-src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/LucasX21s/img_for_blog/blog/img/demo5.png" src="/img/loading.gif" class="lazyload"></a></p><p>Markdown的编辑器很多，可以参考<a href="https://blog.csdn.net/davidhzq/article/details/100815332" target="_blank" rel="noopener">这里</a>。</p><p>在这里我主要推荐一个<a href="https://www.typora.io/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><strong>Typora</strong></a>，因为它长得好看还免费啊！</p><p>会不会继续免费就不知道了。在Typora中是边输入，边显示效果，不像传统的分两页显示。</p><p><a href="https://www.typora.io/img/new/inline.png" data-fancybox="group" data-caption class="fancybox"><img alt title data-src="https://www.typora.io/img/new/inline.png" src="/img/loading.gif" class="lazyload"></a></p><p>emoji只需要打:，然后接个字母就会出现待选的表情，可方便了！</p><p><a href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/LucasX21s/img_for_blog/blog/img/demo6.png" data-fancybox="group" data-caption class="fancybox"><img alt title data-src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/LucasX21s/img_for_blog/blog/img/demo6.png" src="/img/loading.gif" class="lazyload"></a></p>]]></content>
      
      
